      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to find a new home for this absolute beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, so it\u2019s pristine inside and out. You\u2019ve really gotta see it to believe how flawless it is. It drives like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all!",
