    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features pristine individual throttle bodies and a flawlessly synchronized double-VANOS system. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, short-throw engagement, delivering linear power to the rear wheels via the factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis remains structurally impeccable with zero subframe fatigue, supported by an untouched OEM suspension setup that maintains factory-spec damping and rebound. Every bushing, gasket, and seal is in optimal condition, ensuring a visceral, analog driving experience without compromise. Truly a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
